description:
#memories...😍🤘 Graspop Metal Meeting 2019. My favorite festival. Unfortunately, I suspect that all the summer festivals will be cancelled this year. 😔 Okay, just hoping, but the worldwide situation is too crazy.... 🙄
.
I'm just listening to my favorite music the whole day, buying new CDs and hoping that there will come better times for all of us. Maybe a new beginning? New chances? Wish you all the best my friends. ❤
.
